  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Development of a pixel sensor with fine space-time resolution based on SOI technology for the ILC vertex detector</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
